footnotes.text: Acceptable: x >= 90% (Effectiveness), x =< 2% (Miss rate), x =< 5% (False alarm rate)
Marginally acceptable: x >= 80% (Effectiveness), x =< 5% (Miss rate), x =< 10% (False alarm rate)
Unacceptable: x < 80% (Effectiveness), x > 5% (Miss rate), x > 10% (False alarm rate)
